{"text_id":163540,"tokens":["Turning"," the"," other"," cheek"," is"," a"," phrase"," in"," Christian"," doctrine"," that"," refers"," to"," responding"," to"," aggression"," without"," violence","."," The"," phrase"," originates"," from"," the"," Sermon"," on"," the"," Mount"," in"," the"," New"," Testament"," of"," the"," Bible","."," Specifically",","," it"," is"," found"," in"," Matthew"," ","5",":","3","8","-","4","2",","," where"," Jesus"," says",":"," \"","You"," have"," heard"," that"," it"," was"," said",","," '","Eye"," for"," eye",","," and"," tooth"," for"," tooth",".'"," But"," I"," tell"," you",","," do"," not"," resist"," an"," evil"," person","."," If"," anyone"," slaps"," you"," on"," the"," right"," cheek",","," turn"," to"," them"," the"," other"," cheek"," also",".\""," Interpretation"," and"," Application"," The"," phrase"," is"," often"," interpreted"," as"," a"," command"," for"," non","violent"," resistance","."," In"," this"," context",","," \"","turning"," the"," other"," cheek","\""," does"," not"," imply"," passi","vity"," or"," acceptance"," of"," abuse",","," but"," rather"," a"," refusal"," to"," perpetuate"," the"," cycle"," of"," violence"," and"," a"," commitment"," to"," transform"," the"," situation","."," However",","," the"," interpretation"," and"," application"," of"," this"," phrase"," have"," been"," subjects"," of"," debate"," among"," theologians"," and"," scholars","."," Some"," argue"," that"," it"," should"," be"," taken"," literally",","," advocating"," for"," complete"," non","-","violence"," and"," pacif","ism","."," Others"," suggest"," that"," it"," should"," be"," understood"," metaphor","ically",","," representing"," a"," broader"," principle"," of"," non","-","ret","ali","ation"," and"," love"," for"," enemies","."," Influence"," and"," Legacy"," The"," concept"," of"," turning"," the"," other"," cheek"," has"," had"," a"," significant"," influence"," on"," many"," non","violent"," movements"," and"," leaders","